                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Winds southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h becoming light in the late evening.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-04-13T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-04-14T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-04-12T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-04-13T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Light winds becoming southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the early afternoon then becoming light in the evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 9 and 12 with daytime temperatures reaching the low 20s.</text>
